Hi Bruce.  Just a thought.... It&#39;s really sweet of you to make yourself so available to people, 
but if you have members take inquiries of this nature off the boards by having them 
contact your privately, you are limiting the amount of learning that can take place.  There 
are likely &quot;lurkers&quot; here, who will never join or come forward, but could really benefit from 
Lyn&#39;s questions and the answers she receives from the group.  

Taking communication privately also eliminates the possibility for her to receive multiple 
opinions.  (not to imply there isn&#39;t a time for privacy!)  ;0)

Like I said, just a thought.  

Margaret

